@startuml
title NumericField Control Structure
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

class PointerEvent
class NumericFieldInputAdapter
class NumericFieldViewModel
class NumericFieldView
class NumericFieldViewState
class NumericFieldStyle
class NumericFieldRenderStyle
class DefaultNumericFieldRenderer
class ThemeSnapshot

PointerEvent --> NumericFieldInputAdapter : handled directly
NumericFieldInputAdapter --> NumericFieldView : hit test / cursor geometry
NumericFieldInputAdapter --> NumericFieldViewModel : move/press/drag/release/wheel
NumericFieldView --> NumericFieldViewState
NumericFieldView --> ThemeSnapshot
NumericFieldStyle --> NumericFieldViewState
NumericFieldStyle --> ThemeSnapshot
NumericFieldStyle --> NumericFieldRenderStyle
DefaultNumericFieldRenderer --> NumericFieldRenderStyle
@enduml
